s of a volcano, and master the perfect curve on the tracks.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\">COMPETE IN ADRENALINE-FUELLED LIVE EVENTS</h2><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2698940/extras/TCM_Steam_KSP_4.gif?t=1736259250\" /><br>Master all types of vehicles in the Grand Race and finish first among 28 other drivers. Jump into the pure mayhem of Demolition Royale where eight teams battle to be the last one standing. Take on the Summit Clash by completing challenges to dominate the leaderboards!","developers":["Ubisoft Ivory Tower"],"dlc":[2805000,2849030,3251420],"drm_notice":"Battle Eye","ext_user_account_notice":"Ubisoft Account (Supports Linking to Steam Account)","genres":[{"description":"Racing","id":"9"}],"header_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2698940/header.jpg?t=1736259250","is_free":false,"legal_notice":"\u00a9 2023 Ubisoft Entertainment. All Rights Reserved. The Crew, Ubisoft, and the Ubisoft logo are registered or unregistered trademarks of Ubisoft Entertainment in the US and/or other countries.","linux_requirements":[],"mac_requirements":[],"movies":[{"highlight":true,"id":257071477,"mp4":{"480":"http://video.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_trailers/257071477/movie480.mp4?t=1730941457","max":"http://video.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_trailers/257071477/movie_max.mp4?t=1730941457"},"name":"Chase Squad Trailer","thumbnail":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/257071477/13da1ef6ef1b6a39328d9f8f6925e4864fb7ceb9/movie_600x337.jpg?t=1730941457","webm":{"480":"http://video.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_trailers/257071477/movie480_vp9.webm?t=1730941457","max":"http://video.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_trailers/257071477/movie_max_vp9.webm?t=1730941457"}},{"highlight":true,"id":257038867,"mp4":{"480":"http://video.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_trailers/257038867/movie480.mp4?t=1721340053","max":"http://video.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_trailers/257